thread.title: BRIEF-F5 Networks Q1 Earnings Per Share $1.41

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-F5 Networks Q1 Earnings Per Share $1.41
text:
Jan 24 (Reuters) - F5 Networks Inc:
* F5 NETWORKS ANNOUNCES FIRST QUARTER FISCAL 2018 RESULTS * Q1 GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $1.41 * Q1 REVENUE $523.2 MILLION VERSUS I/B/E/S VIEW $522 MILLION
* Q1 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $2.04 -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* Q1 NON-GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $2.26 EXCLUDING ITEMS * ‍FOR Q2 OF FISCAL 2018, ENDING MARCH 31, COMPANY HAS SET A REVENUE GOAL OF $525 MILLION TO $535 MILLION​
* ‍FOR Q2 OF FISCAL 2018, ENDING MARCH 31, COMPANY HAS SET A GAAP EARNINGS TARGET OF $1.66 TO $1.69 PER DILUTED SHARE​
* ‍ FOR Q2 OF FISCAL 2018, ENDING MARCH 31, COMPANY HAS SET A NON-GAAP EARNINGS TARGET OF $2.24 TO $2.27 PER DILUTED SHARE​
* Q2 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $2.12, REVENUE VIEW $528.2 MILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
